    <text id="A7519T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Evans reports on a recent trip.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    <name type="recipient">Miss Mollie Sibert<lb/>Mount Solon<lb/>Va</name>
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1867-09-03">Sept 3 1867</date>
                        <name type="place">Staunton</name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Miss Mollie</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>We <unclear>rived</unclear> home safely and had a <orig reg="very">verry</orig>
                    <orig reg="pleasant">plesent</orig> drive through the <unclear>vall</unclear>
                    which I enjoyed <orig reg="very">verry</orig> much we <unclear>rived</unclear>
                    in Staunton at half past ten. Ella had a good warm Supper <orig reg="prepared"
                        >prepard</orig> for us which Magnus and my self did ample justice <orig
                        reg="to">too</orig> you may look for Magnus down after you in <orig
                        reg="two">too</orig> weeks if not sooner Ella says she <orig reg="don't"
                        >dont</orig> think she will let you stay that long so you will <orig
                        reg="have">haft</orig> to hurry up &amp; get through with your <orig
                        reg="spinning">spining</orig> this week so you can come up with him next
                    week I think I will<pb n="2"/>go over to night and tell Ella to send for you
                    this week for we <orig reg="can't">cant</orig> do with out you I have thought of
                    you all day and <orig reg="wondered">wonderd</orig> if Miss Mollie thought of DH
                    Evans <orig reg="while">whilest</orig> she was <orig reg="spinning"
                    >Spining</orig>. I would like to see you at the Spinning Wheel I know you look
                    interesting. you must Excuse this short note I have been keep so <orig
                        reg="busy">Bussy</orig> since I came home that I have not had time to write
                    I am interrupted ever few <orig reg="minutes">minuts</orig> while I am writing
                    this Excuse all mistakes and write to me soon My love to your Ma, &amp; all
                    of my friends I send a kiss to Miss Mollie all are well </p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Good Buy</salute>
                    <signed>David H. Evans</signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
